[{"text": "Translator: Katheryn McGaffigan\nReviewer: Jenny Zurawell", "start": 0.0, "duration": 7.0}, {"text": "Today I'm going to unpack for you", "start": 15.671, "duration": 2.26}, {"text": "three examples of iconic design,", "start": 17.931, "duration": 2.73}, {"text": "and it makes perfect sense", "start": 20.661, "duration": 1.285}, {"text": "that I should be the one to do it", "start": 21.946, "duration": 2.689}, {"text": "because I have a Bachelor's degree in Literature.", "start": 24.635, "duration": 3.927}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 28.562, "duration": 1.346}, {"text": "But I'm also a famous", "start": 29.908, "duration": 1.423}, {"text": "minor television personality", "start": 31.331, "duration": 2.061}, {"text": "and an avid collector of", "start": 33.392, "duration": 2.07}, {"text": "Design Within Reach catalogs,", "start": 35.462, "duration": 1.576}, {"text": "so I pretty much know", "start": 37.038, "duration": 2.307}, {"text": "everything there is.", "start": 39.345, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "Now, I'm sure you", "start": 40.865, "duration": 1.371}, {"text": "recognize this object;", "start": 42.236, "duration": 1.335}, {"text": "many of you probably saw it", "start": 43.571, "duration": 1.694}, {"text": "as you were landing your private zeppelins", "start": 45.265, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "at Los Angeles International Airport", "start": 46.733, "duration": 2.488}, {"text": "over the past couple of days.", "start": 49.221, "duration": 2.193}, {"text": "This is known as the Theme Building;", "start": 51.414, "duration": 3.343}, {"text": "that is its name for reasons", "start": 54.757, "duration": 1.74}, {"text": "that are still very murky.", "start": 56.497, "duration": 2.751}, {"text": "And it is perhaps", "start": 59.248, "duration": 1.421}, {"text": "the best example we have in Los Angeles", "start": 60.669, "duration": 3.29}, {"text": "of ancient extraterrestrial architecture.", "start": 63.959, "duration": 5.018}, {"text": "It was first excavated in 1961", "start": 68.977, "duration": 2.813}, {"text": "as they were building LAX,", "start": 71.79, "duration": 1.89}, {"text": "although scientists believe that", "start": 73.68, "duration": 1.649}, {"text": "it dates back to the year 2000", "start": 75.329, "duration": 2.587}, {"text": "Before Common Era,", "start": 77.916, "duration": 2.065}, {"text": "when it was used as", "start": 79.981, "duration": 1.341}, {"text": "a busy transdimensional space port", "start": 81.322, "duration": 2.375}, {"text": "by the ancient astronauts", "start": 83.697, "duration": 2.048}, {"text": "who first colonized this planet", "start": 85.745, "duration": 2.082}, {"text": "and raised our species", "start": 87.827, "duration": 1.51}, {"text": "from savagery by giving us", "start": 89.337, "duration": 1.716}, {"text": "the gift of written language", "start": 91.053, "duration": 1.694}, {"text": "and technology and", "start": 92.747, "duration": 1.798}, {"text": "the gift of revolving restaurants.", "start": 94.545, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "It is thought to have been", "start": 97.025, "duration": 3.053}, {"text": "a replacement for the older space ports", "start": 100.078, "duration": 2.622}, {"text": "located, of course, at Stonehenge", "start": 102.7, "duration": 2.853}, {"text": "and considered to be", "start": 105.553, "duration": 1.196}, {"text": "quite an improvement", "start": 106.749, "duration": 1.127}, {"text": "due to the uncluttered design,", "start": 107.876, "duration": 2.077}, {"text": "the lack of druids hanging around all the time", "start": 109.953, "duration": 2.62}, {"text": "and obviously, the much better", "start": 112.573, "duration": 1.789}, {"text": "access to parking.", "start": 114.362, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": "When it was uncovered,", "start": 116.082, "duration": 2.29}, {"text": "it ushered in a new era", "start": 118.372, "duration": 2.206}, {"text": "of streamlined, archaically futuristic design", "start": 120.578, "duration": 3.264}, {"text": "called Googie,", "start": 123.842, "duration": 1.429}, {"text": "which came to be synonymous with", "start": 125.271, "duration": 1.882}, {"text": "the Jet Age, a misnomer.", "start": 127.153, "duration": 2.199}, {"text": "After all, the ancient astronauts who used it", "start": 129.352, "duration": 2.734}, {"text": "did not travel by jet very often,", "start": 132.086, "duration": 1.838}, {"text": "preferring instead to travel by feathered serpent", "start": 133.924, "duration": 3.288}, {"text": "powered by crystal skulls.", "start": 137.212, "duration": 2.656}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 139.868, "duration": 2.282}, {"text": "(Music)", "start": 142.15, "duration": 3.586}, {"text": "Ah yes, a table.", "start": 145.736, "duration": 3.662}, {"text": "We use these every day.", "start": 149.398, "duration": 1.46}, {"text": "And on top of it,", "start": 150.858, "duration": 1.746}, {"text": "the juicy salif.", "start": 152.604, "duration": 2.155}, {"text": "This is a design by Philippe Starck,", "start": 154.759, "duration": 1.454}, {"text": "who I believe is in the audience at this very moment.", "start": 156.213, "duration": 2.063}, {"text": "And you can tell it is a Starck design", "start": 158.276, "duration": 1.915}, {"text": "by its precision, its playfulness,", "start": 160.191, "duration": 3.426}, {"text": "its innovation and", "start": 163.617, "duration": 2.241}, {"text": "its promise of imminent violence.", "start": 165.858, "duration": 3.252}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 169.11, "duration": 2.065}, {"text": "It is a design that challenges your intuition --", "start": 171.175, "duration": 2.958}, {"text": "it is not what you think it is when you first see it.", "start": 174.133, "duration": 2.349}, {"text": "It is not a fork designed", "start": 176.482, "duration": 1.823}, {"text": "to grab three hors d'oeuvres at a time,", "start": 178.305, "duration": 3.374}, {"text": "which would be useful out in the lobby,", "start": 181.679, "duration": 1.776}, {"text": "I would say.", "start": 183.455, "duration": 1.169}, {"text": "And despite its obvious", "start": 184.624, "duration": 1.269}, {"text": "influence by the ancient astronauts", "start": 185.893, "duration": 1.756}, {"text": "and its space agey-ness and tripodism,", "start": 187.649, "duration": 4.19}, {"text": "it is not something", "start": 191.839, "duration": 1.442}, {"text": "designed to attach to your brain", "start": 193.281, "duration": 2.131}, {"text": "and suck out your thoughts.", "start": 195.418, "duration": 2.171}, {"text": "It is in fact a citrus juicer", "start": 197.589, "duration": 2.325}, {"text": "and when I say that,", "start": 199.914, "duration": 1.879}, {"text": "you never see it as anything else again.", "start": 201.793, "duration": 2.792}, {"text": "It is also not a monument to design,", "start": 204.585, "duration": 4.059}, {"text": "it is a monument to design's utility.", "start": 208.644, "duration": 2.593}, {"text": "You can take it home with you,", "start": 211.237, "duration": 2.072}, {"text": "unlike the Theme Building,", "start": 213.309, "duration": 1.828}, {"text": "which will stay where it is forever.", "start": 215.137, "duration": 2.561}, {"text": "This is affordable", "start": 217.698, "duration": 1.574}, {"text": "and can come home with you", "start": 219.272, "duration": 1.609}, {"text": "and, as such, it can sit", "start": 220.881, "duration": 2.06}, {"text": "on your kitchen counter --", "start": 222.941, "duration": 2.388}, {"text": "it can't go in your drawers;", "start": 225.329, "duration": 1.106}, {"text": "trust me, I found that out the hard way --", "start": 226.435, "duration": 2.72}, {"text": "and make your kitchen counter into", "start": 229.155, "duration": 1.986}, {"text": "a monument to design.", "start": 231.141, "duration": 1.573}, {"text": "One other thing about it,", "start": 232.714, "duration": 1.271}, {"text": "if you do have one at home,", "start": 233.985, "duration": 1.546}, {"text": "let me tell you one of the features you may not know:", "start": 235.531, "duration": 2.219}, {"text": "when you fall asleep,", "start": 237.75, "duration": 1.946}, {"text": "it comes alive", "start": 239.696, "duration": 3.391}, {"text": "and it walks around your house", "start": 243.087, "duration": 2.242}, {"text": "and goes through your mail", "start": 245.329, "duration": 1.339}, {"text": "and watches you as you sleep.", "start": 246.668, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 248.918, "duration": 4.182}, {"text": "Okay, what is this object?", "start": 253.1, "duration": 5.604}, {"text": "I have no idea. I don't know what that thing is.", "start": 259.551, "duration": 3.641}, {"text": "It looks terrible. Is it a little hot plate?", "start": 263.192, "duration": 1.802}, {"text": "I don't get it.", "start": 264.994, "duration": 1.408}, {"text": "Does anyone know? Chi?", "start": 266.402, "duration": 2.077}, {"text": "It's an ... iPhone. iPhone.", "start": 268.479, "duration": 1.803}, {"text": "Oh yes, that's right, I remember those;", "start": 270.282, "duration": 2.314}, {"text": "I had my whole bathroom tiles", "start": 272.596, "duration": 1.981}, {"text": "redone with those back in the good old days.", "start": 274.577, "duration": 3.269}, {"text": "No, I have an iPhone. Of course I do.", "start": 277.846, "duration": 2.009}, {"text": "Here is my well-loved iPhone.", "start": 279.855, "duration": 1.716}, {"text": "I do so many things on this little device.", "start": 281.571, "duration": 3.044}, {"text": "I like to read books on it.", "start": 284.615, "duration": 2.01}, {"text": "More than that, I like to buy books on it", "start": 286.625, "duration": 2.512}, {"text": "that I never have to feel guilty about not reading", "start": 289.137, "duration": 1.931}, {"text": "because they go in here and I never look at them again", "start": 291.068, "duration": 1.701}, {"text": "and it's perfect.", "start": 292.769, "duration": 2.946}, {"text": "I use it every day to", "start": 295.715, "duration": 2.156}, {"text": "measure the weight of an ox,", "start": 297.871, "duration": 2.435}, {"text": "for example.", "start": 300.306, "duration": 1.761}, {"text": "Every now and then,", "start": 302.067, "duration": 1.587}, {"text": "I admit that I complete", "start": 303.654, "duration": 1.453}, {"text": "a phone call on it occasionally.", "start": 305.107, "duration": 2.252}, {"text": "And yet I forget about it all the time.", "start": 307.359, "duration": 3.698}, {"text": "This is a design", "start": 311.057, "duration": 1.782}, {"text": "that once you saw it,", "start": 312.839, "duration": 1.621}, {"text": "you forgot about it.", "start": 314.46, "duration": 1.242}, {"text": "It is easy to forget the gasp-inducement", "start": 315.702, "duration": 2.703}, {"text": "that occurred in 2007 when you first", "start": 318.405, "duration": 3.082}, {"text": "touched this thing because it became", "start": 321.487, "duration": 2.77}, {"text": "so quickly pervasive", "start": 324.257, "duration": 1.637}, {"text": "and because of how instantly", "start": 325.894, "duration": 2.426}, {"text": "we adopted these gestures", "start": 328.32, "duration": 2.37}, {"text": "and made it an extension of our life.", "start": 330.69, "duration": 2.995}, {"text": "Unlike the Theme Building,", "start": 333.685, "duration": 2.506}, {"text": "this is not alien technology.", "start": 336.191, "duration": 2.023}, {"text": "Or I should say,", "start": 338.214, "duration": 1.762}, {"text": "what it did was it took technology", "start": 339.976, "duration": 1.799}, {"text": "which, unlike people in this room,", "start": 341.775, "duration": 1.432}, {"text": "to many other people in the world,", "start": 343.207, "duration": 1.094}, {"text": "still feels very alien,", "start": 344.301, "duration": 1.231}, {"text": "and made it immediately and instantly feel", "start": 345.532, "duration": 2.113}, {"text": "familiar and intimate.", "start": 347.645, "duration": 2.239}, {"text": "And unlike the juicy salif,", "start": 349.884, "duration": 2.199}, {"text": "it does not threaten", "start": 352.083, "duration": 1.632}, {"text": "to attach itself to your brain,", "start": 353.715, "duration": 2.192}, {"text": "rather, it simply", "start": 355.907, "duration": 1.968}, {"text": "attaches itself to your brain.", "start": 357.875, "duration": 1.843}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 359.718, "duration": 2.068}, {"text": "And you didn't even notice it happened.", "start": 361.786, "duration": 2.774}, {"text": "So there you go. My name is John Hodgman.", "start": 364.56, "duration": 2.122}, {"text": "I just explained design.", "start": 366.682, "duration": 3.225}, {"text": "Thank you very much.", "start": 369.907, "duration": 1.811}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 371.718, "duration": 3.996}]